title: New: Rustie – Slasherr
content:
Everyone and their momz have been posting this new cut from Rustie, the first leak from his new single, Triadzz/Slasherr, out on Numbers.

Frankly it’s completely worth it, this is big ass beat music at its very best. Happy Fucking Tuesday.
author: 5e9b68b27a1236eccfeb1d24
